title: Football quiz: Can you name every Women's Champions League winner?
body_text:
Can you name every Women's Champions League winner?
- Published
The knockout phase of this season's Women's Champions League begins this week, with both Arsenal and Manchester United in play-off round action.
The English clubs are two of the 12 teams still left in the competition, hoping to become European champions in May.
How well do you know the history of the Women's Champions League, which was known as the Women's Cup from 2002-09? Take our quiz to find out.
